title: Grateful Dead Live at Radio City Music Hall on 1980-10-26
lineage: MAC > Nakamichi CR-5A > Edirol FA-66 > Wavelab > R8Brain > CD-Wave > TLH > FLAC 1644 tagged. Transfer by Andrew F. 10/2011
description:
Set 1

Iko Iko, Dark Hollow, It Must Have Been The Roses, On The Road Again, Jack A Roe, Cassidy, China Doll-> Ripple

Set 2

Jack Straw-> Sugaree, Little Red Rooster, Brown Eyed Women, Let It Grow-> Don't Ease Me In

Set 3

Jam-> Samson & Delilah, Althea, Estimated Prophet-> He's Gone-> Drums-> Not Fade Away-> Stella Blue-> Good Lovin', E: Brokedown Palace

First Set Acoustic

reviews.review_text: Iko All Day This was a nice Sunday night show with Jerry in a mellow mode. Iko, Jack Straw and He's Gone steal the show. Radio City was a high time with the Dead.
